data.description: Appraised for $245,000 on 9/11/2023.  Appraisal in attachments.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! This delightful 2 bedroom, 2 bath starter home is perfect for first-time buyers, investors, or those seeking to downsize. Nestled in the charming community of Orchid Springs in Winter Haven, this home offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.    Step inside and be greeted by a spacious and inviting open living space, ideal for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. The living room boasts soaring ceilings adorned with stunning beams, adding a touch of elegance and character. For added versatility, the kitchen's enclosed lanai features a closet and could easily serve as a third bedroom, providing flexibility to accommodate your unique needs.    Indulge in the pleasures of outdoor living through the sliding glass door in the living room, leading to a screened and covered lanai. Here, you can savor the tranquility of the surroundings while enjoying your favorite beverage or simply unwinding after a long day. And don't forget to explore the expansive yard, offering ample space for various outdoor activities and personalization.    The two-car garage is thoughtfully designed with a screen door, allowing refreshing breezes to flow in while you work inside. The seller has made significant updates to the property, including the installation of new flex pipe throughout the house, from the shutoff valve to every water valve, even extending to the exterior spigots. This ensures peace of mind and a well-maintained plumbing system.    Orchid Springs goes above and beyond to provide a delightful living experience, trash removal, lawn mowing, a clubhouse, and a refreshing community pool. It's the perfect place to unwind, connect with neighbors, and embrace a carefree lifestyle.    The motivated seller has taken the initiative to make further updates to the property, including the removal of the popcorn ceiling, fresh interior wall and ceiling paint, installation of new flooring throughout the home, and a thorough roof cleaning. Updates have been completed, ensuring that you can move in and start enjoying your new home without delay.    Don't let this opportunity pass you by. Schedule a showing today and discover the endless possibilities awaiting you in this remarkable home!
